description:
This is a 21 minute workout called '20 Minute Yoga For Beginners And Athletes' from the channel Breathe and Flow.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

Original workout description: 20 minute yoga flow practice for beginners and athletes on your rest day or to get started with the asana practice.
